OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fdie out during the evening. However,
OL,7,Frain will soon spread northeast,
OL,8,Fbecoming widespread and heavy from
OL,9,Faround midnight, especially over the
OL,10,FMournes. Becoming windy along the
OL,11,FAntrim and Down coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain will become light and
OL,14,Fpatchy during the morning. Becoming
OL,15,Fdry and bright over western counties
OL,16,Fin the afternoon, then across the east
OL,17,Fin the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
