OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of heavy rain move northeast
OL,7,Fduring Sunday. This will be followed
OL,8,Fby bright or sunny spells and showers
OL,9,Fthrough the rest of the period.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
